  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CAIAC Auth - Signin v2.0.0\n\n**Trigger:** POST /caiac/auth/signin\n**Auth:** None — this endpoint IS the auth\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Receive `{ email, password, slug }`\n2. Look up user + client via LEFT JOIN (always returns 1 row)\n3. 401 if user/client not found (`user_found = false`)\n4. 401 if user or client inactive\n5. bcrypt verify password (401 if wrong)\n6. Generate HS256 JWT (1hr expiry)\n7. Return token, webhook_secret, must_change_password, user\n\n**Replaces:** CAIAC Auth - Signin v1.3.1\n(v1.3.1 used HMAC for password check — wrong for human login)\n\n**Credential:** CAIAC Postgres",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "ec152d4e-4a0d-43f8-8d12-0ce079e5d696",
      "name": "About This Workflow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1792, 192]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "caiac/auth/signin",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
